item.title: Introduction to CATALYST
item.description: Welcome to CATALYST! We hope you and your family are safe and healthy this holiday season. First and foremost, letâ€™s address the elephant in the room. What is CATALYST? Formerly known as the Marginalized and Underrepresented Community Alumni Network (MUCAN), the project has recently undergone a name change and will hereafter be titled CATALYST.
